init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The movies you see are not particularly interesting or exciting ones.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When the movie ends, you are once again in blackness.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They smile back at you, but are still a bit worried.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I hope we've managed to make things a little better for you this time around."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: up out of the seats, "Don't worry.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As you lead them to the light, they relax a little and follow you with their eyes.
